en_854818_0	The duty on vehicles with an engine capacity below 1000cc has been amended.
en_854818_1	The duty amendment will be in effect from today.
en_854818_2	The duty on non-hybrid vehicles with an engine capacity lower than 1000cc will be 1.5 million rupees.
en_854818_3	The duty on a hybrid vehicle with an engine capacity lower than 1000cc will be 1.25 million rupees.
en_854818_4	The increased duty will not be applicable for vehicles imported based on letters of credit established on or before August 1st 2018 and cleared from Sri Lanka Customs on or before the 31st January 2019.
en_854818_5	Meanwhile, the duty on cigarettes have also been amended.
en_854818_6	Accordingly, the duty on cigarettes will be increased by 3 rupees and 80 cents from today.
